{"tid":2299803,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"特首稱已覓得330公頃土地興建31萬多公營房屋單位","createTime":"2020-11-25T04:45:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T09:44:55.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"bba8f5325b16046fe0aaa357833abb27c036317c","tid":2299803,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:45:01.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥說，已全數覓得興建316000個公營房屋單位的330公頃土地，可以滿足未來10年，即2021/22至2030/31年約301000個公營房屋單位的需求。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，供應主要來自東涌填海、古洞北/粉嶺北和洪水橋/厦村等新發展區的農地和棕地、多幅改劃作公營房屋的用地、9幅分別位於啟德和安達臣道石礦場改撥為發展公營房屋的用地、粉嶺高爾夫球場部分用地，以及多幅完成檢視具房屋發展潛力的棕地羣。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說，下一年度的「綠置居」約4700個單位將於明年分期出售，當中首批約2100個單位預計於明年5月推出，屆時會聯同已收回的700多個單位一併推售。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561820-20201125.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561820-20201125.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKHfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=24191f79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561820-20201125.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=97b5e000\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561820-20201125.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"ebd1b0b8c9308b928f5d041398195b3313395c23","tid":2299803,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:45:08.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"4335b5cc1ac0c4edd660533ffb31ec56a2a3645e","tid":2299803,"uid":86509,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:45:47.000Z","msg":"啲地變出嚟㗎<br />\n不嬲都有㗎啦戇鳩<br />\n覓覓覓百痴"},{"pid":"8f20acc4cbf98da0f502d5604485222414b9d749","tid":2299803,"uid":237562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:48:30.000Z","msg":"NO ★"},{"pid":"ff3763e22d60dfe4693f43a42ec69b8448d90b52","tid":2299803,"uid":25538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:49:36.000Z","msg":"呢一代年